				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'm a big fan of epic fantasy series.  Some of my favorites not listed all ready are:
<br />

<br />
David Eddings - 
<br />
   The Belgariad (5 Books)
<br />
   The Mallorean (5 Books) - Follows the events in the Belgiariad
<br />
   The Elenium (3 Books) - New series, no ties to the previous two series
<br />
   The Tamuli (3 Books) - Follows the events of the Elenium
<br />

<br />
Melanie Rawn - Can't remember the name of the trilogy, but I think the first book is named The Dragon Prince.
<br />

<br />
Margaret Weiss and Tracy Hickman - Doomsword Trilogy (older one), and Rose of the Prophet Trilogy.
<br />

<br />
Of course, the LotR books if you haven't read them yet.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=436860" target="_blank" class="postlink">Losher</a> 59 Vah Shir Beastlord
